To get all Employees :- 
	select Get operation and enter "http://localhost:8081/api/employees" as url

To post an Employee :-
	select Post operation and enter "http://localhost:8081/api/employees" as url
	Add body accordingly
	
To get Employee by ID :-
	select Get operation and enter "http://localhost:8081/api/employees/ID" as url
	
To update an Employee :-
	select Put operation and enter "http://localhost:8081/api/employees/ID" as url
	Add body accordingly
	
To delete an Employee :-
	select Delete operation and enter "http://localhost:8081/api/employees/ID" as url